race.comment: VIERI (1) raced on the speed and lifted to score by a head this trip to continue his outstanding recent form. Carries more weight back in grade but rates to deliver the hat-trick. THE ALBION (4) scored by 1L last start over this journey in a 58. Was quickly back on track and flies this course and distance. Maps for the run of the race and Todd is a key jockey engagement. JULY (3) doesn't win very often but ran a nice race last time out over 1300m at this track. Steps up to a mile for the first time and gets in well with the 3kg claim. Worth keeping onside. BEAU FACTOR (2) was plain last time but his effort prior in a 70 would have him in the mix.
